<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2694] Instance state not recomputed after reconfiguration when the instance is stopped</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2694</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a component instance is stopped and reconfigured, the instance state is not recomputed. The instance must be restarted with the new configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
